1. 添加OpenFOAM源
sudo add-apt-repository http://dl.openfoam.org/ubuntu

2. 添加库的密钥文件(gpg.key)
sudo sh -c "wget -O - http://dl.openfoam.org/gpg.key | apt-key add -"

3. 更新软件为最新版本
sudo apt-get update

4.安装OpenFOAM-7和ParaView5.6.0
sudo apt-get -y install openfoam7

5. 添加环境变量
echo 'source /opt/openfoam7/etc/bashrc' >> $HOME/.bashrc
source $HOME/.bashrc

6. 测试是否安装成功
icoFoam -help
